  "legal_bases": [
    {
      "type": "act",
      "identifier": "The Minister for Foreign Affairs listed this entity on 21 November 2003 under section 15(1) of the Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 (CotUNA), pursuant to Australia's obligations under UNSC resolution 1373 (2001). See Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 List 2003 (No. 3) [F2021L00628, Gazette No. S 426, 21 November 2003].  The Minister declared on 07 November 2019, pursuant to section 15A(2) of CotUNA, that this listing would continue to have effect. Relisted on 6 November 2022, 13/09/2025 in Charter of the United Nations (Listed Persons and Entities) Amendment (No. 2) Instrument 2025",
      "title": "The Minister for Foreign Affairs listed this entity on 21 November 2003 under section 15(1) of the Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 (CotUNA), pursuant to Australia's obligations under UNSC resolution 1373 (2001). See Charter of the United Nations Act 1945 List 2003 (No. 3) [F2021L00628, Gazette No. S 426, 21 November 2003].  The Minister declared on 07 November 2019, pursuant to section 15A(2) of CotUNA, that this listing would continue to have effect. Relisted on 6 November 2022, 13/09/2025 in Charter of the United Nations (Listed Persons and Entities) Amendment (No. 2) Instrument 2025"
    }
